{"tid":2448778,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"牛牛被綁GPS頸圈以至淚流不止 組織倡另覓方法偵測流浪牛","createTime":"2021-03-16T07:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T06:28:37.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d3a8a433e67b0b3c4c79030ec18f5dd7f28834","tid":2448778,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FhPituAvEaOc.ruGCX83Hg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/00558b20-85f5-11eb-b335-4da3bfc44a28\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFhPituAvEaOc.ruGCX83Hg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F00558b20-85f5-11eb-b335-4da3bfc44a28&h=d09ece3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東網昨(14日)揭發西貢有牛隻被政府套上追蹤位置的GPS頸圈致「寢食難安」，甚至痛苦至流淚。記者今(15日)到現場視察，只見<strong><span class=\"red\">有約50頭牛正在食草及休息，而涉事牛隻則躺在地上，期間仍不時落淚，眼睛兩側有淚痕</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span class=\"red\">記者嘗試了解其頸圈鬆緊度，發現僅「攝」到2隻手指。</span></strong>有組織今(15日)表示，反對政府為牛隻加上頸圈，質疑有關方法是否唯一能夠偵測野外牛隻的方法。有網民批評負責的漁農自然護理署漠視動物感受，未有善待動物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pC4qQqWetkgFPyyGHi3u_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/37c214c0-85f5-11eb-bffe-b539160fec7d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpC4qQqWetkgFPyyGHi3u_Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F37c214c0-85f5-11eb-bffe-b539160fec7d&h=17e1b0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事牛隻至今仍不時落淚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大嶼山愛護水牛協會主席何來表示，原則上反對政府為牛隻加上頸圈，認為目前署方的解釋未夠說服力，又質疑署方如何能夠確保牛隻權利受到保護，並認為政府應向市民公開計劃詳情，以作交代。<br />\n<br />\n西貢十四鄉村牛關注組成員則於社交平台上指，若牛隻並非從小習慣佩戴頸圈，至長大後才佩戴，必然會利用所有辦法掙脫，建議為減少牛隻不適，應為其佩戴有彈性的頸圈。涉事牛隻「崩崩」曾掙脫約7條頸圈，曾於冬天佩戴具彈性的尼龍頸圈，但因應天氣回暖，目前已改作佩戴全彈性的頸圈，盼牠不會因此而受傷。另有網民留言直斥，<strong><span class=\"red\">牛隻能夠感受愛與被愛，質疑漁護署未有善待動物。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注動物權益的議員葛珮帆亦指，明白港府為牛隻套上頸圈，是為了方便監察及照顧牠們，但她認為，若有關設備令牛隻痛苦難耐，甚至難以進食，則令外界感到殘酷，亦可能有市民認為是虐待動物，認為當局應作檢討，研究可否以其他方法達致相同目標。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，漁護署早在2012年為牛隻套上GPS頸圈，為追蹤牛隻的活動範圍，有助掌握流浪牛的行走路線、去留及棲息地點等資料，又可讓政府規劃牛隻遷移地點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q3XPXQH3V8Wwsuc43DlHEw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/42b768d0-85f5-11eb-8fdf-8c47325ef545\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq3XPXQH3V8Wwsuc43DlHEw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F42b768d0-85f5-11eb-8fdf-8c47325ef545&h=7aa1e3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者嘗試了解頸圈鬆緊度，發現僅攝到2隻手指。"},{"pid":"2bcbf217840bee9761ad31fade6e02fbc2cf57b9","tid":2448778,"uid":37959,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"以為你講富途牛牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85591305614c5781432023052316a13222ff5455","tid":2448778,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:24:20.000Z","msg":"牛眼淚藍色架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352b9fb3c6029351216b16fea6a4a40c93d481da","tid":2448778,"uid":24750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"尋晚東張閪望仲話隻牛淚線發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2142face8cd0b007f11b39f911b75d844dc